Will you please ban me?

30:00.909 --> 30:02.331
- Oh, I don't think
it works that way.

30:02.431 --> 30:03.932
What happened?

30:04.032 --> 30:06.214
- I texted Eric last night

30:06.314 --> 30:07.975
at 10:00

30:08.075 --> 30:09.657
and asked him what he was doing

30:09.757 --> 30:11.218
and this is what he wrote back.

30:11.318 --> 30:14.061
- "Watching 'Chicago Fire'
with my wife."

30:14.161 --> 30:15.942
Ah.

30:16.042 --> 30:18.825
You didn't know he was...
- Uh-uh.

30:18.925 --> 30:21.267
And I don't know
why it should matter.

30:21.367 --> 30:23.949
The man lives in Minnesota

30:24.049 --> 30:25.831
and I am nowhere near ready

30:25.931 --> 30:29.053
for anything anyway, but...

30:31.295 --> 30:32.316
I don't know.

30:32.416 --> 30:33.958
- I...

30:34.058 --> 30:36.360
I think this is a great thing.

30:36.460 --> 30:37.961
- Why?

30:38.061 --> 30:40.083
So David can rest easy?

30:40.183 --> 30:41.644
- No, no, no.

30:41.744 --> 30:44.367
Because it proves
there's still

30:44.467 --> 30:46.168
that part of you inside
that can

30:46.268 --> 30:48.250
feel that way again.

30:48.350 --> 30:50.292
That's huge.

30:50.392 --> 30:52.053
- Wait, who are you?

30:52.153 --> 30:54.055
And what have you done
with the real Emily?

30:54.155 --> 30:55.376
- Ah.

30:55.476 --> 30:56.977
Turns out because
of these happy pills

30:57.077 --> 30:58.459
the psychiatrist gave me,

30:58.559 --> 30:59.940
I suddenly have these things

31:00.040 --> 31:02.262
called hope and optimism.

31:02.362 --> 31:05.224
It's uncomfortable.

31:05.324 --> 31:06.946
- Ah.

31:07.046 --> 31:09.048
Oh.

31:12.611 --> 31:15.113
Yo, Simon. Welcome.
What can I do for you?

31:15.213 --> 31:16.794
- We had a 10:00.

31:16.894 --> 31:18.316
- Oh, yeah.

31:18.416 --> 31:20.197
I stopped wearing watches.

31:20.297 --> 31:21.558
What's up?

31:21.658 --> 31:23.160
- I want to create
the incubation program

31:23.260 --> 31:25.041
here for
small businesses, okay?

31:25.141 --> 31:26.723
Focused on people of color

31:26.823 --> 31:28.324
and other marginalized groups,

31:28.424 --> 31:29.845
and the first company

31:29.945 --> 31:31.487
I wanna bring into the fold

31:31.587 --> 31:32.968
is Sky Talker.

31:33.068 --> 31:34.129
- [sighs]
- Come on.

31:34.229 --> 31:35.450
- But we were gonna
have so much fun

31:35.550 --> 31:37.132
bleeding them dry in court.

31:37.232 --> 31:38.613
- Danny, uh-uh,

31:38.713 --> 31:41.135
they're three young

31:41.235 --> 31:43.417
Black entrepreneurs
who deserve to be elevated

31:43.517 --> 31:45.139
and empowered,

31:45.239 --> 31:47.240
not eaten up and spit out
by a big business.

31:49.722 --> 31:51.864
- All right, let's say

31:51.964 --> 31:54.567
we buy that company and we put
you in charge of all of it?

31:59.211 --> 32:01.633
Oh, but then what about
your current job?

32:01.733 --> 32:04.035
- I think this is where
I want focus my energy.

32:04.135 --> 32:05.556
This is what I'm
passionate about,

32:05.656 --> 32:07.658
and I think it's a better
use of my talent.

32:10.660 --> 32:12.982
- Who can say no to that?

32:15.064 --> 32:17.466
Not me.

32:19.268 --> 32:20.649
- Come on, man.

32:20.749 --> 32:21.610
- We can hug?
- Yeah.

32:21.710 --> 32:23.131
- Okay.

32:23.231 --> 32:24.732
- My man.

32:24.832 --> 32:26.614
- Oh, uh, did you run
this by Zoey yet?

32:26.714 --> 32:29.016
- Oh, because she's...

32:29.116 --> 32:30.457
- Your boss?

32:30.557 --> 32:32.299
- Oh, no, but she'll be fine.

32:32.399 --> 32:35.181
She's a very understanding
and rational person.

32:35.281 --> 32:36.623
- How are we gonna do this?

32:36.723 --> 32:38.384
Bomb threat?
Drive onto the tarmac?

32:38.484 --> 32:40.506
Oh, are we gonna stuff some
drugs into Rose's backpack?

32:40.606 --> 32:42.508
- I know we did not drive all
the way here without a plan.

32:42.608 --> 32:44.109
- Since when did we have time
for a plan?

32:44.209 --> 32:45.150
- Whoa.

32:45.250 --> 32:47.152
- Ah! Okay.

32:47.252 --> 32:49.033
Let me think.

32:49.133 --> 32:50.354
- Oh, well you better
think quick,

32:50.454 --> 32:52.496
'cause they're right there.

32:56.099 --> 32:57.480
- Screw it.
I'm just gonna wing it.

32:57.580 --> 32:58.721
- Go, best friend!

32:58.821 --> 33:01.103
Go, best friend!

33:09.230 --> 33:14.175
- ♪ When a man loves a woman ♪

33:14.275 --> 33:18.098
♪ Can't keep his mind
on nothing else ♪

33:18.198 --> 33:23.302
♪ He'd change for world
