33:23.402 --> 33:25.905
♪ If she is bad ♪

33:26.005 --> 33:28.947
♪ He can't see it ♪

33:29.047 --> 33:32.831
♪ She could do no wrong ♪

33:32.931 --> 33:34.992
♪ Turn his back
