33:47.823 --> 33:53.088
♪ Trying to hold on
to what he needs ♪

33:53.188 --> 33:55.570
♪ He'd give up all-- ♪

33:55.670 --> 33:58.413
- What happened?

33:58.513 --> 34:01.235
- I just heard Max
sing a heart song to Rose.

34:03.357 --> 34:05.999
He really loves her.

34:11.203 --> 34:13.565
It's over.

34:27.657 --> 34:29.399
- Hey.

34:29.499 --> 34:31.080
Can I ask you
a personal question?

34:31.180 --> 34:32.762
Woman to woman.

34:32.862 --> 34:35.284
Everyone's talking about you
and Simon breaking up.

34:35.384 --> 34:36.565
- Oh.

34:36.665 --> 34:37.686
You all--

34:37.786 --> 34:39.408
- All knew. Yeah.
You hid nothing.

34:39.508 --> 34:41.690
And I'm just wondering

34:41.790 --> 34:44.212
was working together
the reason it imploded?

34:44.312 --> 34:47.014
Are Tobin and I just, like,

34:47.114 --> 34:49.236
doomed from the start?

34:54.240 --> 34:56.422
- Sorry.

34:56.522 --> 34:59.505
I'll be right back.

34:59.605 --> 35:03.188
- ♪ And did you think this
fool could never win? ♪

35:03.288 --> 35:07.311
♪ Look at me,
I'm coming back again ♪

35:07.411 --> 35:11.915
♪ I got a taste of love
in a simple way ♪

35:12.015 --> 35:15.238
♪ And if you need to know
while I'm still standing ♪

35:15.338 --> 35:19.782
♪ You just fade away ♪

35:22.264 --> 35:24.646
♪ Don't you know
I'm still standing ♪

35:24.746 --> 35:27.489
♪ Better than I ever did ♪

35:27.589 --> 35:30.211
♪ Looking like
a true survivor ♪

35:30.311 --> 35:32.213
♪ Feeling like a little kid ♪

35:32.313 --> 35:33.574
♪ Yeah ♪

35:33.674 --> 35:35.856
♪ I'm still standing ♪

35:35.956 --> 35:38.498
♪ After all this time ♪

35:38.598 --> 35:40.820
♪ Picking up the pieces
of my life ♪

35:40.920 --> 35:43.422
♪ Without you on my mind ♪

35:43.522 --> 35:45.904
♪ I'm still standing ♪

35:46.004 --> 35:49.608
♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah ♪

36:00.777 --> 36:02.198
- As we were saying.

36:02.298 --> 36:05.081
Working with Simon
is not what broke us up.

36:05.181 --> 36:08.123
We just...

36:08.223 --> 36:10.966
weren't meant to be.

36:11.066 --> 36:13.908
Not everybody is.

36:17.792 --> 36:19.453
And that's okay.

36:19.553 --> 36:22.576
Just go into it
with an open mind

36:22.676 --> 36:25.899
and a little bit of faith,

36:25.999 --> 36:28.281
and the rest will
work itself out.

36:32.564 --> 36:34.066
Why did you summon us here?

36:34.166 --> 36:35.507
- You're selling the house,
aren't you?

36:35.607 --> 36:37.148
Please don't, we'll take it.
We'll sublet Zoey's room.

36:37.248 --> 36:39.150
All that rent
can be yours tax free.

36:39.250 --> 36:41.272
- Great to know
if I get in a pinch, but no,

36:41.372 --> 36:43.233
I'm not selling the house.

36:43.333 --> 36:46.196
I just wanted to inform
all of you,

36:46.296 --> 36:49.239
especially in light of the way

36:49.339 --> 36:51.921
David behaved in regards
to Eric Shepard.

36:52.021 --> 36:53.682
- One of his many aliases.

36:53.782 --> 36:57.566
- That I'm...

36:57.666 --> 37:00.408
starting to think

37:00.508 --> 37:03.211
about the possibility

37:03.311 --> 37:06.093
of considering

37:06.193 --> 37:09.436
putting myself
back out there again.

37:11.798 --> 37:14.220
And I hope that
you all will be open

37:14.320 --> 37:16.942
and accepting

37:17.042 --> 37:19.805
with me on this journey.

37:22.887 --> 37:24.709
- Well, you know I'm down.

37:24.809 --> 37:26.390
- Mom.

37:26.490 --> 37:30.514
I support whatever
it is you want.

37:30.614 --> 37:32.936
I just want you to be happy.

37:38.260 --> 37:39.802
- Honestly, I just--

37:39.902 --> 37:42.204
Mom, I just want
you to be happy too.

37:42.304 --> 37:44.326
It just might take me, like,

37:44.426 --> 37:46.448
a second to completely
wrap my head around it.

37:46.548 --> 37:48.129
- I get it.

37:48.229 --> 37:49.570
because

37:49.670 --> 37:51.452
it's so weird

37:51.552 --> 37:53.413
for all of us,

37:53.513 --> 37:56.256
but...

37:56.356 --> 37:59.459
I need to keep living my life.

37:59.559 --> 38:01.701
Your dad wanted all of us

38:01.801 --> 38:04.343
to keep living our lives.

38:04.443 --> 38:06.224
Like he said,

38:06.324 --> 38:09.187
we just gotta carry on.

38:09.287 --> 38:12.190
[gentle music]

38:12.290 --> 38:19.175
♪ ♪

38:43.316 --> 38:46.699
- Mean, y'all, this is...
[continues indistinctly]

38:46.799 --> 38:53.685
♪ ♪

39:20.388 --> 39:21.689
- You know,
you could keep trying,

39:21.789 --> 39:23.010
but that thing's never actually

39:23.110 --> 39:25.112
gonna make you invisible.

39:26.233 --> 39:28.234
- Max?

39:31.637 --> 39:34.019
I don't understand.

39:34.119 --> 39:36.141
You didn't go to New York
with Rose?

39:36.241 --> 39:38.744
- No, I broke it off with her
at the airport.

39:38.844 --> 39:41.426
She could tell
I was distracted

39:41.526 --> 39:43.928
thinking about someone else.

39:45.329 --> 39:47.271
And we decided
it wasn't fair, you know?

39:47.371 --> 39:49.453
To her or me.

39:50.894 --> 39:53.276
Listen, I can't know

39:53.376 --> 39:55.078
what's going on in your head,

39:55.178 --> 39:57.520
and maybe there'll
always be this

39:57.620 --> 39:59.281
power imbalance between
the two of us

39:59.381 --> 40:00.722
because of that,

40:00.822 --> 40:02.003
but I don't care.

40:02.103 --> 40:04.566
- Max Richman.

40:04.666 --> 40:06.647
I am not

40:06.747 --> 40:08.369
gonna to be scared anymore.

40:08.469 --> 40:11.171
Okay? I'm not gonna
run away from you

40:11.271 --> 40:13.713
because I'm afraid
of feeling too much.

40:14.834 --> 40:17.016
I...

40:17.116 --> 40:19.098
I have

40:19.198 --> 40:21.300
no idea what

40:21.400 --> 40:24.062
the universe

40:24.162 --> 40:27.185
has in store for you and me,

40:27.285 --> 40:29.387
but...

40:29.487 --> 40:32.149
what I do know

40:32.249 --> 40:34.391
is there is someone
very special

40:34.491 --> 40:37.354
looking over us, so...

40:37.454 --> 40:39.736
I guess what
I'm trying to say is...

40:42.058 --> 40:44.960
[energetic music]

40:45.060 --> 40:49.764
♪ ♪

40:49.864 --> 40:55.809
♪ Moving forward using
all my breath ♪

40:55.909 --> 41:01.654
♪ Making love to you
was never second best ♪

41:01.754 --> 41:03.736
♪ I saw the world ♪

41:03.836 --> 41:07.980
♪ Flashing all around
your face ♪

41:08.080 --> 41:11.783
♪ Never really knowing
it was always ♪

41:11.883 --> 41:14.105
♪ Mesh and lace ♪

41:14.205 --> 41:20.030
