41:57.002 --> 41:59.464
♪ You've seen the difference ♪

41:59.564 --> 42:03.788
♪ And it's getting
better all the time ♪

42:03.888 --> 42:09.713
♪ There's nothing
you and I won't do ♪

42:09.813 --> 42:14.256
♪ I'll stop the world
and melt with you ♪

42:17.299 --> 42:19.421
I want to be with you.

42:20.542 --> 42:22.924
And somehow,

42:23.024 --> 42:25.726
together

42:25.826 --> 42:27.448
we will find a way

42:27.548 --> 42:30.611
